  "prompt": "What is best free one page theme for WordPress?",
  "response": "There are several great free one-page themes for WordPress that you can consider. Here are a few popular options:\n\n1. **Astra** - A lightweight and customizable theme that is perfect for one-page websites. It\u2019s compatible with popular page builders like Elementor and Beaver Builder.\n\n2. **Hestia** - A modern theme that comes with a one-page layout. It\u2019s versatile and suitable for startups, portfolios, and corporate sites.\n\n3. **OceanWP** - This theme offers a one-page demo and is highly customizable. It works well with page builders and is responsive and SEO-friendly.\n\n4. **Zerif Lite (or Zelle Lite)** - A clean and professional one-page theme that is suitable for businesses and freelancers. It offers a smooth scrolling effect and is easy to customize.\n\n5. **One Page Express** - Specifically designed for creating stunning one-page sites. It features a live editor that allows for easy customization.\n\n6. **Shapely** - A feature-rich one-page theme with a responsive design. It\u2019s great for personal and professional websites and supports various plugins for additional functionality.\n\n7. **Sydney** - A powerful business theme that offers a full-screen slider and is well-optimized for one-page layouts. It provides customization options using the WordPress Customizer.\n\nThese themes often come with their own demo content and customization options, so you can choose one that best fits your needs and aesthetic preference. Always check recent reviews and updates to ensure the theme is still actively maintained and supported.",
